children.name: SELECT "statuses"."id" FROM "statuses" LEFT OUTER JOIN "status_stats" ON "status_stats"."status_id" = "statuses"."id" WHERE "statuses"."account_id" = $1 AND "statuses"."id" <= $2 AND (COALESCE(status_stats.favourites_count, 0) < 5) AND "statuses"."visibility" != $3 AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM status_pins pin WHERE pin.account_id = statuses.account_id AND pin.status_id = statuses.id)) AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM favourites fav WHERE fav.account_id = statuses.account_id AND fav.status_id = statuses.id)) AND "statuses"."deleted_at" IS NULL AND (NOT EXISTS (SELECT 1 FROM bookmarks bookmark WHERE bookmark.account_id = statuses.account_id AND bookmark.status_id = statuses.id)) ORDER BY "statuses"."id" ASC LIMIT $4
